INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,819,1584,'und',0,'<p>In addition to analyzing data from institutional systems, participating colleges contribute data to a longitudinal (multi-year) national database.&nbsp; The Achieving the Dream Database provides a mechanism to collect data on cohorts of students attending a participating Achieving the Dream college for the first time.&nbsp; Only students who seek a credential (a degree or a certificate) are tracked.&nbsp; Unlike the Department of Education database, IPEDS, the&nbsp;Achieving the Dream&nbsp;Database tracks both full-time and part-time students.</p><p>Each fall, participating colleges provide student record data (with unique, non-Social-Security Number identifiers) on new cohorts of entering students as well as data on prior year cohorts.&nbsp; The&nbsp;Achieving the Dream&nbsp;Database includes the following data elements:</p><ul><li>Demographic data &ndash; sex, age and race/ethnicity;</li><li>Zip code &ndash; to create a proxy for socioeconomic status;</li><li>Academic preparation (if available) &ndash; high school diploma, GED or other; date of receipt of high school degree; admission test result; remediation referral status; previous college credits transferred; previous postsecondary degree or certificate;</li><li>Student performance &ndash; number of credits enrolled and completed each semester, developmental education enrollment and completion each semester, gateway course enrollment and completion each semester (e.g., college algebra or college English) and grades each semester in developmental education and gateway courses;</li><li>Financial aid &ndash; application and receipt status first semester only, total amount of grant aid and loan aid by source each semester;</li><li>Outcomes &ndash; degree or certificate attainment, transferred to other college</li></ul><p>The data collected in the&nbsp;Achieving the Dream&nbsp;Database emphasize key measures of student success &ndash; outcomes in developmental courses, outcomes in gatekeeper courses, persistence, and graduation. Student outcomes can be further analyzed by race, ethnicity, and other student characteristics.</p>','','filtered_html');
INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,820,1585,'und',0,'<p>The&nbsp;Achieving the Dream&nbsp;Database contains more than 1.5 million student records submitted by Achieving the Dream Colleges.&nbsp; The database is used for research by two partners of Achieving the Dream, JBL Associates and the Community College Research Center.&nbsp;</p><ul><li>JBL Associates&nbsp;uses&nbsp;the&nbsp;Achieving the Dream&nbsp;Database to produce a bi-monthly newsletter called &ldquo;Data Notes&rdquo;.&nbsp; In each Data Note, JBL Associates focuses on a topic related to student outcomes at the Achieving the Dream Colleges.</li><li>Community College Research Center (CCRC) uses the&nbsp;Achieving the Dream&nbsp;Database for research projects focused on community college issues including access and equity; the high school-to-college transition; institutional mission and governance; programs and practice; and workforce education.</li></ul>','','filtered_html');
INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,821,1586,'und',0,'<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://bi.achievingthedream.org/MicroStrategy/asp/\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.achievingthedreammembers.org/members/datatoolslogin.jpg\" /></a></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">The data tool allows members to view student achievement data. It emphasizes Achieving the Dream&#39;s key measures of student success. It includes institutional and benchmark dashboards (for peer comparisons), and analytical tools to generate ad-hoc reports. </font></p><ul><li><a class=\"skdgWidgetGeneratedBtn skdgWidgetTrigger\" face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" font=\"\" href=\"javascript:;\" size=\"2\" style=\"border-radius: 5px 5px 5px 5px; -moz-border-radius: 5px 5px 5px 5px; -webkit-border-radius: 5px 5px 5px 5px;background-color:#ffffff; font-size:12px; height:40px; width:120px; color: #green\">Book a Webinar Now</a></li><li><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\"><a href=\"/achieving_the_dream_data_access_tool_resources\" target=\"_blank\">View training videos and other resources</a></font></li></ul><p><strong>Interventions to Improve Student Outcomes</strong></p><p>Interventions to Improve Student Outcomes <font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">As the Achieving the Dream Initiative evolves, it is increasingly important to ensure consistency in documenting and reporting on institutions&#39; intervention strategies and evaluation results. The national Achieving the Dream partners have developed this online tool to help institutions document and track the progress of their interventions. The tool has two components:</font></p><p class=\"style1\"><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">I. The&nbsp;</font><a href=\"http://achievingthedreammembers.org/Intervention/InterventionHome1.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Intervention Collection Tool\"><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">Intervention Collection Tool</font></a><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">: Achieving the Dream colleges may enter their interventions here. Each college has a point person who is responsible for entering and keeping their institution&#39;s information up-to-date. &nbsp;</font></p><p class=\"style1\"><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">II. The&nbsp;</font><a href=\"http://achievingthedreammembers.org/Intervention/Reports/InterventionSearch.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Intervention Report Tool\"><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">Intervention Report Tool</font></a><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">: All posted interventions may be viewed here. &nbsp;</font></p><p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">Resources</font></p><ul dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left: 80px;\"><li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 40px;\"><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/Users_Manual.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"User Manual\"><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">User Manual</font></a><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></div></li><li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt 40px;\"><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/Intervention_Tool_Checklist.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Intervention Tool Checklist\"><font face=\"Verdana, Helvetica\" size=\"2\">Intervention Tool Checklist</font></a></div></li></ul>','','filtered_html');
