INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','hidden_page',0,3171,5699,'und',0,'<h2>Purpose</h2><p>The Spring Retreat is intended to address the following four overall objectives:</p><ol><li>To welcome new leadership coaches and data coaches.</li><li>To share the latest developments in ATD to ensure that leadership coaches and data coaches are well informed during site visits.</li><li>To continuously improve the practice of coaching.</li><li>To share information about the new college cohort.</li></ol><h2>Desired Outcomes</h2><p>For the 2012 Spring Retreat, all participants will:</p><ul><li>Learn about the incoming 2012 cohort</li><li>Understand ATD resources, technologies, and staff</li><li>Discuss new grant opportunities for colleges</li><li>Brainstorm on new &ldquo;peer coaching&rdquo; model</li><li>Discuss data &amp; technology to support colleges and coaches</li><li>Share best practices</li><li>Discuss and update leadership coach and data coach role descriptions</li><li>Understand data technologies for the 2012 cohort</li><li>Review and prioritize recommendations from the Fall 2011 Retreat to incorporate into plans for 2012/2013 academic year.</li></ul><p>Additionally, Data Coaches will:</p><ul><li>Discuss general data coaching topics</li><li>Design data templates for annual reporting</li></ul><p>Additionally, Leadership Coaches will:</p><ul><li>Discuss general coaching topics</li></ul>','','filtered_html');
