INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','hidden_page',0,3183,5934,'und',0,'<p>The official Achieving the Dream, Inc. logo is the cornerstone of the entire Achieving the Dream identity system. The symbol can be seen as both a wing and a stairway. These icons give the feeling of movement and freedom and symbolize moving up and reaching aspirational goals. Your first step should be to download this logo&rsquo;s Identity Standards Guide, which references rules regarding the use of this signature.</p><p><a href=\"/sites/default/files/achieving_the_dream_identity_standards_guide.pdf\">Download the Achieving the Dream Identity Standards Guide</a>.</p><h3>Horizontal Signature</h3><ul><li><h3><img alt=\"\" class=\"image-inline_photo_float_right\" src=\"http://achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/styles/inline_photo_float_right/public/images/ATD-HSig-3272Kpng.png\" title=\"Horizontal Signature\" /></h3><a href=\"/sites/default/files/ATD-HSig-3272K.eps\">Download this as an EPS file</a>. EPS files are a standard format for graphics professionals and those more familiar with publishing. This format allows for quality usage at any size enlargement.</li><li><a href=\"/sites/default/files/images/ATD-HSig-3272Kpng.png\">Download this as a PNG file</a>. PNG is a standard cross-platform (Mac or PC) format that can be used on the Web.</li><li><a href=\"/sites/default/files/images/ATD-HSig-3272Kjpg.jpg\">Download this as a JPEG file</a>. Please note that JPEG files cannot be significantly enlarged beyond the original signature size contained within these original files. These JPEGs are 72 dpi.</li></ul><h3><img alt=\"\" class=\"image-inline_photo_float_right\" src=\"http://achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/styles/inline_photo_float_right/public/images/ATD-VSig-3272Kpng.png\" title=\"\" />Vertical Signature</h3><ul><li><a href=\"/sites/default/files/ATD-VSig-3272K.eps\">Download this as an EPS file</a>. EPS files are a standard format for graphics professionals and tho