INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','hidden_page',0,3184,5935,'und',0,'<p>It is our hope that your institution will proudly portray its inclusion in the ATD national network. We have created an endorsement phrase and logo that can be incorporated into your existing communications and marketing vehicles. Once your institution has joined ATD, you are free to refer to your college as An Achieving the Dream&trade; Institution in your communications materials, including your stationery, website, promotional and informational materials, email signatures, etc. Your first step should be to download the Endorsement Guidelines, which references rules regarding the use of this phrase and logo.</p><p><a href=\"/sites/default/files/achieving_the_dream_endorsement_guidelines.pdf\">Download the Achieving the Dream Endorsement Guidelines</a>.</p><h3>Horizontal Signature</h3><ul><li><img alt=\"\" class=\"image-inline_photo_float_right\" src=\"http://achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/styles/inline_photo_float_right/public/images/ATDendorsed-HSig-3272K.png\" title=\"\" /><a href=\"/sites/default/files/ATDendorsed-HSig-3272K.eps\">Download this as an EPS file</a>. EPS files are a standard format for graphics professionals and those more familiar with publishing. This format allows for quality usage at any size enlargement.</li><li><a href=\"/sites/default/files/images/ATDendorsed-HSig-3272K.png\">Download this as a PNG file</a>. PNG is a standard cross-platform (Mac or PC) format that can be used on the Web.</li><li><a href=\"/sites/default/files/images/ATDendorsed-HSig-3272Kjpg.jpg\">Download this as a JPEG file</a>. Please note that JPEG files cannot be significantly enlarged beyond the original signature size contained within these original files. These JPEGs are 72 dpi.</li></ul><h3><img alt=\"\" class=\"image-inline_photo_float_right\" src=\"http://achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/styles/inline_photo_float_right/public/images/ATDendorsed-SigSticker-3272K.