INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,3481,7944,'und',0,'<p><strong>Challenge:</strong><br />Despite the implementation of innovative and promising student success interventions at Achieving the Dream Institutions, the reach of these interventions is too often relatively modest compared to the total number of students at the college in need of the supports. The Achieving the Dream National Reform Network is committed to investigating ways to scale promising interventions to ensure that more, and ultimately most, students attain the skills and credentials necessary for success in the global economy.</p><p><strong>Solution:</strong><br />Through a competitive grant program funded by the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation and administered by Achieving the Dream, Inc., a select group of Achieving the Dream Leader Colleges &ndash; known for their commitment to student-centered evidence-based reforms and outstanding increases in student outcomes &ndash; will be awarded $200,000 - $250,000 each to expand their proven interventions to reach a significantly large population of their students. The program &ndash; called the <strong><em>Catalyst Fund </em></strong>&ndash; will award four Achieving the Dream Leader Colleges from November 1, 2012 to October 31, 2014 with a significant investment to spur the expansion of interventions. Recipients will be expected to support two additional years of implementation after the initial grant funds expire.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Proposal Templates:</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/ATD%20Catalyst%20Fund%20RFP_Templates_ENTER%20COLLEGE%20NAME_DATE.xls\" title=\"Catalyst Fund RFP Templates\">Catalyst Fund RFP Templates</a></li></ul><p><strong>Catalyst Fund Resources:</strong></p><p><strong>Application:</strong></p><ul><li><em style=\"background-color:transparent;font-family:OpenSansItalic,Helvetica,Arial,\'Nimbus Sans L\',sans-serif;font-style:normal\">The deadline for the Catalyst Fund proposals has passed but you can view the&nbsp;</em>RFP&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/ATD%20Catalyst%20Fund%20RFP_FINAL.doc\" style=\"color:rgb(121,162,178);text-decoration:none\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Here!\">Here</a>.<ul><li><strong style=\"font-family:OpenSansSemiBold,Helvetica,Arial,\'Nimbus Sans L\',sans-serif;font-weight:normal\">Proposal Templates:&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/ATD%20Catalyst%20Fund%20RFP_Templates_ENTER%20COLLEGE%20NAME_DATE.xls\" style=\"color:rgb(121,162,178);text-decoration:none\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Catalyst Fund RFP Templates\">Catalyst Fund RFP Templates</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/cdat_loss%26momentum_r101_0.pdf\" title=\"Loss Momentum Framework \">Loss Momentum Framework</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/resources/M2M.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"More to Most: Scaling Up Effective Community College Practices\">More to Most: Scaling Up Effective Community College Practices</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/resources/CuttingEdgeNo2Scaling.pdf\" title=\"Scaling Community College Interventions \">Scaling Community College Interventions </a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/ATD_Measures_and_the_Loss_Momentum_Framework_FINAL.pdf\" title=\"ATD Measures and Loss Momentum Framework\">ATD Measures and Loss Momentum Framework</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/August_LC_CC_PowerPoint3_compressed%281%29.pdf\" title=\"August Leader College Call Presentation on the Catalyst Fund\">August Leader College Call Presentation on the Catalyst Fund</a></li><li><em>*<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jx1Buuh16XI&amp;feature=plcp\">Listen to the August Leader College call on the Catalyst Fund</a></em></li></ul><p><strong>Background on The Achieving the Dream Grant Program:</strong><br />The Catalyst Fund is just one of the opportunities available through the growing Achieving the Dream Grant Program, which provides resources for Achieving the Dream Institutions to incorporate cutting-edge research and scale promising student success interventions with the aim of accelerating and sustaining improved student outcomes. &nbsp;Achieving the Dream Institutions should look for additional grant opportunities from Achieving the Dream in the future.</p><p><strong>Questions: </strong><br />Questions regarding the Catalyst Fund and the RFP can be sent to:&nbsp;Sarah Hollister,&nbsp;Associate Director of Programs,&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:catalyst@achievingthedream.org\">catalyst@achievingthedream.org</a>.&nbsp;</p>','','filtered_html');
