INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,3646,8454,'und',0,'<p>DREAM 2013<br />Achieving the Dream&rsquo;s Annual Meeting on Student Success<br />February 5 &ndash; 8, 2013<br />Hilton Anaheim<br />Anaheim, California</p><h2>Call for Workshop Proposals</h2><p>Achieving the Dream, Inc. (ATD) is pleased to extend the Call for Workshop Proposals for <strong>DREAM</strong> <strong>2013. <font color=\"#ff0000\"><span style=\"line-height:20.866666793823242px;font-size:14px;font-family:OpenSansRegular,Helvetica,Arial,\'Nimbus Sans L\',sans-serif\">Call for Workshop Proposals for&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"line-height:20.866666793823242px;font-size:14px;font-family:OpenSansSemiBold,Helvetica,Arial,\'Nimbus Sans L\',sans-serif;font-weight:normal\">DREAM</strong><span style=\"line-height:20.866666793823242px;font-size:14px;font-family:OpenSansRegular,Helvetica,Arial,\'Nimbus Sans L\',sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"line-height:20.866666793823242px;font-size:14px;font-family:OpenSansSemiBold,Helvetica,Arial,\'Nimbus Sans L\',sans-serif;font-weight:normal\">2013 </strong><font style=\"line-height:20.866666793823242px;font-size:14px;font-family:OpenSansRegular,Helvetica,Arial,\'Nimbus Sans L\',sans-serif\"><b style=\"font-family:OpenSansSemiBold,Helvetica,Arial,\'Nimbus Sans L\',sans-serif;font-weight:normal\">are now closed</b></font></font></strong><strong><font color=\"#ff0000\"> </font></strong></p><p>The emphasis of DREAM 2013, as in past years, is &ldquo;Equity and Excellence,&rdquo; and we will focus on student success and closing achievement gaps for historically underserved student populations. All workshops must be highly interactive, provide evidence to support claims of success, and convey information and tips that will help others apply lessons learned.</p><p>The purpose of DREAM 2013 is to:</p><ul><li>Reflect on and share lessons from Achieving the Dream experiences;</li><li>Deepen understanding of ways to increase student success and equity in student outcomes;</li><li>Increase capacity for data analysis, program evaluation, and data-informed decision-making;</li><li>Develop peer connections that lead to year-round peer learning; and</li><li>Continue building the Achieving the Dream community of learners.</li></ul><p><strong><u>Important Dates</u></strong></p><ul><li><strong>COB Friday, September 28, 2012&ndash; </strong>Deadline for Workshop Proposals</li><li><strong>Monday, November 5, 2012 &ndash; </strong>Applicants are notified of proposal acceptance status</li><li><strong>Friday, January 11, 2013 &ndash; </strong>Workshop leaders email electronic versions of handouts and PowerPoint presentations to <a href=\"mailto:dream@achievingthedream.org\">dream@achievingthedream.org</a>.</li></ul><h2><a href=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/Call_for_Workshop_Proposal_Guidelines_FINAL%282%29.pdf\" title=\"Review the Call for Workshop Proposals Guidelines \">Review the Call for Workshop Proposals Guidelines </a></h2><h2><a href=\"https://www.conferenceabstracts.com/cfp2/login.asp?EventKey=QHWXYJSE\">Begin your proposal submission</a></h2><h2>Watch the DREAM Workshop Proposal Webinar</h2><p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/9eA_o-T0HLA\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>','','full_html');
