INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,3919,9115,'und',0,'<h2>Registration Deadline is Tuesday, January 22, 2013.</h2><p>Online registration for DREAM 2013, Achieving the Dream&rsquo;s Annual Meeting on Student Success, is now open! This is a new procedure, so please read the following information carefully.</p><h2>Procedure</h2><p>Each active Achieving the Dream Institution and Founding Partner has been allocated a certain number of complimentary registration slots in the online registration system and will need a complimentary code to redeem this slot. The complimentary code was included in the invitation email sent to the Achieving the DreamCore Team. Please consult with your team members to determine who should register as &ldquo;complimentary.&rdquo; Anyone registering after the institution&rsquo;s complimentary slots have been redeemed must pay the $525 registration fee. No code is necessary for the $525 fee.</p><h2>Rates</h2><p><strong>Regular Rate</strong>: $525 per person. This rate includes the entire DREAM 2013: Tuesday reception and dinner and Wednesday through Friday meals and events.</p><p><strong>Tuesday Reception and Dinner Rate</strong>: $75 per person. This rate includes the reception and opening dinner on Tuesday ONLY.</p><p><strong>Wednesday Rate including Tuesday evening</strong>: $330 per person. This rate includes the reception and opening dinner on Tuesday AND meals and events all day Wednesday.</p><p><strong>Wednesday Rate</strong>: $250 per person. This Rate includes meals and events for Wednesday only.</p><p><strong>Thursday Rate</strong>: $250 per person. This rate includes meals and events for Thursday only.</p><p><strong>Substitution and Cancellation Policy</strong>: Any paid participant who does not attend DREAM 2013 is responsible for the registration fee if the registration is not cancelled by Friday, January 18, 2013. A 20% cancellation fee will apply. <strong>No refunds will be issued for cancellations received after January 18, 2013</strong>.</p><p>Participant substitutions can be made at any time by emailing <a href=\"mailto:dream@achievingthedream.org\">dream@achievingthedream.org</a>.</p><h2>Allocated Complimentary Registration Slots</h2><p><a href=\"/sites/default/files/Comp_Slots_DREAM_2013.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Please click here</a> to see how many complimentary slots are assigned to your institution or organization.</p><h2>What Your Registration Includes</h2><ul><li>Admission to the Achieving the Dream Learning Community</li><li>Selected conference materials</li><li>Hospitality<ul><li>Tuesday: Reception and Dinner</li><li>Wednesday: Breakfast and Lunch</li><li>Thursday: Breakfast and Lunch</li><li>Friday: Breakfast and Boxed Lunch</li><li>Daily coffee breaks</li></ul></li></ul><h2>How to Register</h2><p>To register for DREAM 2013 online, please <em>thoroughly read</em> and follow the instructions below.</p><ol><li><a href=\"http://www.cvent.com/events/dream-2013-achieving-the-dream-s-annual-meeting-on-student-success/event-summary-bc0c22a9699b4e15a6cb1e68e6391397.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">CLICK HERE TO BEGIN REGISTRATION</a>. The registration form will appear in a new window, so you can easily come back and refer to these instructions.</li><li>Select the &ldquo;Register!&rdquo; button that appears on the bottom right-hand side of the page.</li><li>Fill out your first name, last name, and email address and click &ldquo;Next.&rdquo;<ul style=\"\"><li>If you are registering for someone else, please enter THEIR name and email address, not yours.</li></ul></li><li>REGISTRATION INFORMATION: Complete the personal and contact information. If you are in our database, these fields will be pre-populated. Please edit and update any fields as necessary. All fields in RED are required.</li><li>Complete the registration questions.</li><li>In the bottom section, you have the option to send this meeting invitation to other colleagues. Otherwise, click &ldquo;Next&rdquo; to proceed.</li><li>ITEM SELECTION: Select one rate, then click Next to proceed. If you are using a complimentary code, please select the Regular Rate. Upon check out, you will redeem your code for the complimentary rate.</li><li>Select your (optional) Pre-Meeting Workshop. If you do not plan to attend a Pre-Meeting Workshop, scroll to the bottom and click &ldquo;Next.&rdquo;</li><li>SUMMARY: This page allows you to review your registration and make any edits before the payment page. This is also the section where you can <strong>add and register multiple people</strong>. Click on the &ldquo;Add Person&rdquo; button that is on the left-hand side of the page. The system will take you to the beginning of the process.</li><li>PAYMENT: This page displays your registration selections. If a payment is required, select your method and enter the information below. Fields and options marked with an asterisk (*) are required to complete your registration. Please click &ldquo;Finish&rdquo; to complete your registration and a confirmation email will be sent to you.</li></ol><h2>Payment</h2><p>A credit card or check is required to pay for all DREAM 2013 and Pre-Meeting Workshop registration fees.</p><p>If you are paying by check, send the check with a copy of the registration form or online confirmation page to the address below.</p><p>Achieving the Dream, Inc.<br />8455 Colesville Road, Suite 900<br />Silver Spring, MD 20910<br />ATTN: DREAM 2013 &ndash; Accounting</p><p><strong>Payment is due no later than Friday, March 1, 2013</strong>. Outstanding balances not received by Friday, March 1, 2013 will be charged a $100 late fee.</p><p><em>NOTE: Failure to send the registration form or confirmation page with your check will delay your registration.</em></p><p>Questions? Please email <a href=\"mailto:dream@achievingthedream.org\">dream@achievingthedream.org</a>.</p>','','filtered_html');
INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,3920,9117,'und',0,'<h2>Hotel Reservations</h2><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"image-inline_photo_float_right\" src=\"http://www.achievingthedream.org/sites/default/files/styles/inline_chart_center/public/images/New%20Exterior.JPG\" title=\"\" width=\"300\" />A discounted room rate at the Hilton Anaheim has been secured for DREAM 2013, Achieving the Dream&rsquo;s Annual Meeting on Student Success, participants. <strong>All participants must make their own hotel reservations.</strong> The cut-off date for hotel reservations is <strong>Friday, January 11, 2013.</strong></p><h2>Hotel Costs</h2><p>All DREAM 2013 participants must cover their own hotel expenses. Achieving the Dream grant funds or institutional funds reserved to support Achieving the Dream work may be used to cover hotel and travel expenses. Information about the hotel, as well as the dedicated website for making hotel reservations, is outlined below. Note: The DREAM 2013 rate is not posted on the general hotel website.&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Single Room: $149.00 plus tax</li><li>Double Room: $149.00 plus tax</li><li>Additional Person: $20.00 plus tax</li></ul><p>The DREAM 2013 rate includes complimentary high-speed Internet access in all sleeping rooms.</p><p><strong>The cut-off date for making hotel reservations is Friday, January 11, 2013</strong>. Room reservations received after the reservation cut-off date will be confirmed on a space-available basis at the group rate. All reservations must be accompanied by the registrant&rsquo;s complete address, along with a first night&rsquo;s deposit plus tax or a major credit card. Deposits are refundable only for cancellations occurring up to 48 hours prior to arrival. <strong>Please note: Call the hotel directly to cancel hotel reservations. Achieving the Dream will not cancel hotel reservations for DREAM attendees.</strong></p><p>To receive the negotiated discount rate, DREAM 2013 participants may make their hotel reservations at the Hilton Anaheim by phone or online. Refer to &ldquo;Achieving the Dream&rdquo; when making reservations by phone. For technical questions regarding the hotel&rsquo;s reservations webpage, please contact the hotel directly.</p><p><strong>Hilton Anaheim<br />(877) 776-4932</strong><br /><a href=\"http://resweb.passkey.com/go/DREAM2013\" target=\"_blank\">http://resweb.passkey.com/go/DREAM2013</a></p><ul><li>The conference rate is guaranteed for three days before and after DREAM 2013, subject to the hotel&rsquo;s availability.</li><li>The hotel check-in time is 4:00 pm and check-out time is 12:00 noon. You will be required to present a credit card when you check in.</li><li>Deposits are refundable only for cancellations occurring up to 48 hours prior to arrival. <strong>Please note: Call the hotel directly to cancel hotel reservations. Achieving the Dream will not cancel hotel reservations for DREAM attendees.</strong></li><li>Early Departure Fee &ndash; In the event you must depart the hotel prior to your reserved check-out date, the hotel will add an early check-out fee of $100.00 to your account. To avoid the fee, notify the hotel at or before check-in of any change in planned length of stay.</li></ul><p>If you have any questions regarding the online registration or hotel reservations, please contact Cristina Blanco at 240-450-3834 or <a href=\"mailto:cblanco@achievingthedream.org\">cblanco@achievingthedream.org</a>.</p>','','filtered_html');
INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,3921,9118,'und',0,'<h2>Air Travel</h2><p>All attendees are responsible for their own travel arrangements. The closest airports are the John Wayne Airport/Orange County (SNA), Long Beach Airport (LGB), and Los Angeles International Airport (LAX).</p><h2>Ground Transportation</h2><p>John Wayne Airport/Orange County (SNA)</p><ul><li>Distance from Hotel: 14 miles</li><li>Drive Time: 20 minutes</li><li>Typical Minimum Charge for Super Shuttle: $13.00 (per person)</li><li>Typical Minimum Charge for Taxi: $35.00 (per person)</li></ul><p>Long Beach Airport (Daugherty Field) (LGB)</p><ul><li>Distance from Hotel: 14 miles</li><li>Drive Time: 25 minutes</li><li>Typical Minimum Charge for Super Shuttle: $33.00 (per person)</li><li>Typical Minimum Charge for Taxi: $50.00 (per person)</li></ul><p>Los Angeles International Airport (LAX)</p><ul><li>Distance from Hotel: 35 miles</li><li>Drive Time: 40-50 minutes</li><li>Typical Minimum Charge for Super Shuttle: $16.00 (per person)</li><li>Typical Minimum Charge for Taxi: $95.00 (per person)</li></ul>','','filtered_html');
